    {
      "beat_id": "B04",
      "act": "THE PROBLEM",
      "type": "GRAPHIC",
      "name": "TheTrial",
      "narration_text": "Anthropic's 2026 randomized trial. Fifty-two junior engineers. One group used an AI assistant. The other wrote every line by hand. Same problem. Same time. Then: a comprehension quiz.",
      "shot": {
        "type": "GRAPHIC",
        "source": "own",
        "motion": "drawon"
      },
      "estimated_duration_s": 14,
      "audio_file": "../vox-fluency-learning/mp3/beat-B04.mp3",
      "actual_duration_s": 15.49,
      "locked": true,
      "source_clip": "../vox-fluency-learning/clips/B04.mp4",
      "source_audio": "../vox-fluency-learning/mp3/beat-B04.mp3"
    },
    {
      "beat_id": "B05",
      "act": "THE PROBLEM",
      "type": "GRAPHIC",
      "name": "TheGap",
      "narration_text": "Hand-coding group: 67 percent. AI-assisted group: 50 percent. Seventeen points. Nearly two letter grades. One variable: who did the executing.",
      "shot": {
        "type": "GRAPHIC",
        "source": "own",
        "motion": "drawon"
      },
      "estimated_duration_s": 11,
      "audio_file": "../vox-fluency-learning/mp3/beat-B05.mp3",
      "actual_duration_s": 11.0,
      "locked": true,
      "source_clip": "../vox-fluency-learning/clips/B05.mp4",
      "source_audio": "../vox-fluency-learning/mp3/beat-B05.mp3"
    },
    {
      "beat_id": "B06",
      "act": "THE MECHANISM",
      "type": "GRAPHIC",
      "name": "InsideTheGroup",
      "narration_text": "But inside the AI group, behavior split the outcome cleanly. Some engineers interrogated the model \u2014 reading every answer, asking why, pushing back. Others delegated \u2014 paste the problem, accept the output, move on.",
      "shot": {
        "type": "GRAPHIC",
        "source": "own",
        "motion": "drawon"
      },
      "estimated_duration_s": 16,
      "audio_file": "../vox-fluency-learning/mp3/beat-B06.mp3",
      "actual_duration_s": 14.16,
      "locked": true,
      "source_clip": "../vox-fluency-learning/clips/B06.mp4",
      "source_audio": "../vox-fluency-learning/mp3/beat-B06.mp3"
    },
    {
      "beat_id": "B07",
      "act": "THE MECHANISM",
      "type": "GRAPHIC",
      "name": "ThreeBarReveal",
      "narration_text": "Interrogators scored 65 to 86 percent \u2014 matching the hand-coders. Delegators scored 24 to 39 percent. Same tool. Same task. Opposite result.",
      "shot": {
        "type": "GRAPHIC",
        "source": "own",
        "motion": "drawon"
      },
      "estimated_duration_s": 13,
      "audio_file": "../vox-fluency-learning/mp3/beat-B07.mp3",
      "actual_duration_s": 11.89,
      "locked": true,
      "source_clip": "../vox-fluency-learning/clips/B07.mp4",
      "source_audio": "../vox-fluency-learning/mp3/beat-B07.mp3"
    },
    {
      "beat_id": "B08",
      "act": "THE MECHANISM",
      "type": "DOCUMENT",
      "name": "TheMechanism",
      "narration_text": "Execution and comprehension are different events. AI handles execution. Comprehension is built by the struggle to understand what was produced.",
      "shot": {
        "type": "GRAPHIC",
        "source": "own",
        "motion": "hold"
      },
      "estimated_duration_s": 11,
      "audio_file": "../vox-fluency-learning/mp3/beat-B08.mp3",
